Author: tradewithnando#0001
Content:
Simple understanding analysis on **$BABA** as we go into tomorrow. This is for those who are in the play with me! 

Before the opening we saw a huge spike, not just on Alibaba but a majority of tickers in the market all due to news based on the Chip Sector of Tech. I‚Äôd like to say this is what mainly drove the market towards the upside! Now at times we will see clear healthy run ups, but in this case we will need some further consolidation/retrace before price moving any higher due to the quickness of the upside move. 

For tomorrow, we‚Äôd like to see price hold above **$103** and eventually a break through the **104** level which is what will open the door to **$108**. Mainly looking for some continuation after the beat down these last few weeks on these Chinese stocks! @here

Content:
Get this consistency down and that +$55 then turns into +$550 (10 contracts) +$1100 (20 contracts) etc **In minutes** 

You just need to get the motions down first. Walk before you try to run. This is very simply to get down if you just give yourself more time to learn. This is why we are done in one or two trades normally. We have spent the years building our accounts. First, comes consistency. Can‚Äôt look at this as a get rich quick scheme.
